I lost my father when I was 29, way too early.

34:24.008 --> 34:27.112
Lost my mother, lost my sister, my whole family.

34:27.152 --> 34:29.055
I remember, but guess what?

34:30.136 --> 34:30.977
They're waiting for me.

34:32.059 --> 34:34.161
There's going to be a reuniting.

34:35.403 --> 34:36.144
A reuniting.

34:36.204 --> 34:37.586
I'm thanking God for that.

34:38.210 --> 34:39.852
Because you know what I know the Bible says?

34:40.133 --> 34:48.503
The Bible says your loved ones, your loved ones, this is Bible that have preceded you are gonna greet you when you go through those pearly gates.

34:48.564 --> 34:49.284
Did you know that?

34:50.506 --> 34:53.470
Oh yeah, oh yeah, the Bible has a whole lot to say about that.

34:53.490 --> 34:57.215
You know, when a Christian dies, angels escort you to heaven.

34:58.176 --> 35:05.746
And then the Bible says that when you enter heaven, your loved ones will be there to greet you and you'll be reunited with them.

35:06.018 --> 35:08.682
Oh, if I think about that for a while, I get pumped.

35:09.603 --> 35:10.324
I get stirred up.

35:10.404 --> 35:11.325
I get lifted up.

35:12.066 --> 35:18.916
And then not only, not only reserve a place and not only reuniting of my family and my friends, but a release.

35:20.017 --> 35:23.442
I'm going to be released from this flesh and all the habits.

35:24.283 --> 35:26.947
You know, Paul said the things that I don't want to do, I do.

35:27.728 --> 35:29.771
And the things that I should do, I don't.

35:30.472 --> 35:31.373
I can relate to that.

35:31.393 --> 35:32.274
How about you?

35:32.546 --> 35:46.266
There's going to be a release because in that place, there'll be no sin, no sorrow, no sickness, no rape, no incest, no abortion, no divorce, no lack, no racism, no bigotry, no wars.

35:47.207 --> 35:51.414
In that place, come on, somebody will be released.

35:53.096 --> 35:57.202
And then not only that, I thank God that I'm going to be rewarded.

35:57.794 --> 36:02.979
You realize that we're saved by grace, not by works, but you're rewarded for your works.

36:04.020 --> 36:11.128
That's why you want to do as much as you can for the Lord, storing up treasure in heaven because heaven is not a communist country.

36:11.428 --> 36:13.050
It's not an entitlement country.

36:13.310 --> 36:14.851
We'll all have different rewards.

36:14.891 --> 36:17.334
We all won't be in the same subdivision doing the same thing.

36:17.374 --> 36:20.277
We're in the same clothes, driving the same angel car.

36:22.259 --> 36:25.362
You're rewarded according to your works.

36:26.050 --> 36:31.937
It's so important that you and I understand that there are different rewards for what we do down here.

36:31.957 --> 36:37.164
So you really want to work for the Lord with the right motive to get the right.

36:37.184 --> 36:41.489
When I thank God for that, well, I can't stay down in the moldy grubs.

36:42.270 --> 36:46.656
And then last but not least, reassigned, reassigned.

36:47.937 --> 36:48.878
What do I thank God for?

36:49.399 --> 36:50.400
My place in heaven.

36:51.722 --> 36:53.584
It's a place reserved just for me.

36:54.565 --> 36:55.026
Wow.

36:55.618 --> 36:58.522
There's reuniting there.

36:58.582 --> 37:02.026
There's a reunion going on there.

37:02.046 --> 37:05.591
There is reassignment that we're looking at going on there.

37:06.211 --> 37:07.113
And what do you mean, Pastor?

37:07.393 --> 37:08.735
We're all gonna be working.

37:09.756 --> 37:10.897
Don't throw rocks at me.

37:10.917 --> 37:12.259
We're all gonna be working.

37:13.080 --> 37:15.343
Work is a four-letter word, but it's not a cuss word.

37:15.383 --> 37:16.765
We're all gonna be working.

37:17.446 --> 37:23.954
Really, Pastor, in the beginning, in the garden, Adam and Eve, you realize they were supposed to live forever, right?

37:24.258 --> 37:25.499
They were supposed to live forever.

37:26.240 --> 37:31.925
And what God do, He created a garden, He put them there and He said this, work it, work it.

37:32.846 --> 37:35.068
So God is the God of work.

37:35.108 --> 37:41.074
So we're not gonna have church services for eternity and be with a harp and a choir and a white robe.

37:41.394 --> 37:44.097
There's gonna be work for you to do, work for me to do.

37:44.137 --> 37:51.384
The Bible says we're gonna rule and reign with Him over universes, over worlds throughout eternity.

37:52.265 --> 37:53.586
When I think about that,

37:54.242 --> 37:59.088
I thank God for heaven because that's my home and I'm just passing through.

37:59.869 --> 38:06.737
Five things to thank God for when you think you have nothing to thank God for.

38:06.777 --> 38:07.958
I'm done.

38:07.978 --> 38:09.400
Did I help anybody today?

38:11.522 --> 38:13.765
Thanks for watching this week's message.

38:14.466 --> 38:18.290
One way for you to connect your church in Iraq is through the guidance for your classes.

38:18.754 --> 38:26.586
These classes are designed to teach you about the culture, mission, and values of church in Iraq, and about your God-given design.

38:27.427 --> 38:34.017
You can take these classes anytime by going to our website at cotr.org slash, God is for you.

38:34.718 --> 38:42.269
And if you want to know about all the incredible things we have here at church in Iraq, make sure to visit our website at cotr.org.

38:43.050 --> 38:45.714
And never forget, God is for you.

